window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Life was simpler when someone was around to tell him what to do. With a band of Adventurers looking to him for direction, whether he likes it or not, Trent Embra needed to figure out how to lead them.</b></p> <p>But how was he supposed to lead when there were so many things Trent hadnâ€™t figured out for himself?</p> <p>An unidentifiable seed in his Storage, and whispers in his head, Trent points his team west towards the wilds. It was as good a direction as any. Maybe in uncivilized lands, Trent would learn what it meant to be an Adventurer and sort through what mattered most.</p>"; 
